* CSSN sign-on success screen (rendered after a successful CSSN auth).
MAP CSSNOK SIZE 24x80
  FIELD AT 0,0  LEN 30 PROT BRIGHT COLOR=BLUE     "BRICKS Transaction Server"
  FIELD AT 0,60 LEN 5  PROT COLOR=BLUE            "TERM="
  INPUT TERMID  AT 0,65 LEN 8  PROT COLOR=BLUE
  INPUT MSG     AT 5,0  LEN 75 PROT BRIGHT COLOR=RED
  FIELD AT 22,0 LEN 30 PROT COLOR=BLUE            "Press ENTER to continue."
ENDMAP
